			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:137/ss:d">subsection (d)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking <quote>section 23(d)</quote> and inserting
